<p>
    To use our packages with Composer, add the following to your
    <code>composer.json</code> to enable our repository:
</p>

<pre class="highlight javascript"><code>"repositories": [
    {
        "type": "composer",
        "url": "https://packages.zendframework.com/"
    }
],</code></pre>

<p>
    You can then add any of our packages to your require list. For
    example:
</p>

<pre class="highlight javascript"><code>"require": {
    "zendframework/zend-config": "2.0.*",
    "zendframework/zend-http": "2.0.*"
},</code></pre>

<p>
    Run the install command to resolve and download the dependencies:
</p>

<pre class="highlight bash"><code>php composer.phar install</code></pre>

